This optical delivery system was mounted on a 2D translation stage, though
 as the beam passes off a scanning galvo, this is used to scan either in
 the X or Y direction for data acquisition and only one axis of the translation
 stage was used for lateral movement of the imaging system.
 The control of the scanning systems was undertaken by a personal computer
 with a LabView based imaging program.
